text: St. Patrick's Day Slam (2022) was a professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It was held on March 16, 2022 at the Freeman Coliseum in San Antonio, Texas. The event aired as special episode of Dynamite. It was the second St. Patrick's Day Slam event held by AEW. The main event of the show saw Thunder Rosa defeated Dr. Britt Baker, D.M.D. in a Steel Cage match to become the new AEW Women's World Champion.
